                <note rend="inline" type="source">124.936/4–2349: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in China</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Stuart</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Nanking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1949-04-23T17:00:00+08:00"
                            >April 23, 1949—5 p. m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received April 23—8:59 a. m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>840. April 23 burned bulk of classified files. Small amount classified material,
                    currently needed codes and code machine not being destroyed for time being.</p>
                <p>Sent Department; repeated Shanghai 426, AmEmb Canton 288.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stuart</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
